  "design_notes": "The chart is built for a medium difficulty, matching the steady 85 BPM swing of the song. The intro starts sparse to ease the player in, using simple steps with virtual grid anchors to prevent long pauses. The energy scales up at bar 13 with the first drop, incorporating holds to map the sustained synth vocals. The midsection provides a brief breather before ramping back up into a rhythmic stream for the outro peak, ending with dramatic final taps.",
